# Dashboard Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- React Query for data fetching
- Zustand for state (if needed)
- Prisma + PostgreSQL (Supabase)

## Code Style
- Functional components with TypeScript
- Named exports for components
- React Query for all API calls
- Keep components focused and small
- Always use shadcn/ui components

## Priorities
- Sports: NBA > NFL > others
- Watchlist: Anime > Movies > Shows
- Games section
- Manual refresh only for sports

## File Organization
- Components: src/components/{feature}/ComponentName.tsx
- API routes: src/app/api/{feature}/route.ts
- Types: src/types/{feature}.ts
- API clients: src/lib/api/{feature}.ts

## Authentication
- Simple password (env: DASHBOARD_PASSWORD)
- Session in localStorage

## APIs
- Sports: ESPN API
- Anime: Jikan API (https://api.jikan.moe/v4)
- Movies/Shows: TMDB API
- Games: RAWG API
- Weather: OpenWeatherMap

